Package: FINEMAPMISS
Type: Package
Title: Fine-mapping meta-analyses with missing information
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joonas Kartau and Matti Pirinen
Maintainer: The package maintainer <joonas.kartau@helsinki.fi>
Description: (REF TO ORIG FINEMAP) This package contain functions for running FINEMAP-MISS, a Bayesian variable selection method for genetic fine-mapping. FINEMAP-MISS differs from previous methods, as it allows for the combination of multiple datasets across biobanks, while also functioning with missing data. 
